AutoCAD DXF
HVAC Systems Design
Date: 2026-03-04
Version: 3.0

MECHANICAL SYSTEMS DESIGN
===========================

Central Chiller System:
- Type: Centrifugal Chiller (2 units N+1)
- Capacity: 2250 kW each (4500 kW total)
- Refrigerant: HFC-134a (zero ODP)
- COP: 4.0+ at delta T 6°C

Boiler System:
- Type: Water-tube gas-fired boiler (2 units N+1)
- Capacity: 1100 kW each (2200 kW total)
- Fuel: Mains natural gas
- Efficiency: 94% seasonal
- Modulation: 15-100% turndown

Pump Systems:
- Chilled Water Pump: 160 m3/h @ 200 kPa
- Condenser Water Pump: 240 m3/h @ 250 kPa
- Hot Water Pump: 80 m3/h @ 150 kPa
- All pumps: Variable frequency drives (VFD)

Cooling Tower:
- Type: Induced draft cooling tower
- Capacity: 4500 kW
- Water Flow: 240 m3/h
- Height: 12 meters
- Noise Rating: 78 dB(A) @ 1m

Ductwork Distribution:
- Supply Mains: DN800-DN1000 (galvanized steel)
- Return Ducts: DN900-DN1200 (flexible returns)
- Exhaust Ducts: DN600-DN800 (rooftop exhausts)
- Total Ductwork: 8500 meters
- Velocity: 5-6 m/s (noise controlled)
- Insulation: 50mm polyurethane, R-2.0 minimum

Terminal Units:
- Variable Air Volume (VAV) boxes: 156 total
- Damper Control: Proportional electric
- Pressure Sensor: In each zone
- Low-flow alarm: Energy efficiency indicator

Filtration:
- Main Filter: MERV-13 prefilters
- Replacement: Every 3 months
- Bypass: 2% maximum leakage
- Pressure Drop: 150 Pa clean, 250 Pa dirty limit

Ventilation:
- Outdoor Air: 8-15 L/s per person (variable)
- Minimum Outside Air: 20% during operation
- Makeup Air: 100% exhausted air balanced
- Economizer: Outdoor air free cooling when < 18°C

Sound Attenuation:
- Main Duct Silencers: Lined at source
- Duct Lining: 50mm foam-faced fiberglass
- Terminal Units: Integral silencers
- Target Noise: ≤ 35 dB(A) occupied spaces

Control System:
- Building Management System: DDC control
- Setpoints: Adjustable via touch panel
- Occupancy: Auto override outside hours
- Demand Reset: Temperature optimization
- Energy Monitoring: Real-time consumption display

Maintenance Access:
- Service Doors: Every 15m ductwork runs
- Filter Access: Ground-level, safe access
- Equipment Rooms: Minimum 3m x 4m per floor
- Clearance: 1.2m on all sides for service

System Performance:
- System Response: < 5 minutes to setpoint
- Uniform Comfort: ±1°C throughout building
- Energy Efficiency: 40% below baseline
- Peak Load Reduction: 15% via chilled beam assist

Commissioning:
- Air Balance: Performed to ±10% variance
- Controls Verification: Full functional test
- Performance Testing: 24-hour operation
- Training: Building operations staff
Status: READY FOR COMMISSIONING
